  "text": "The calculated p-values were corrected for multiple tests using the Benjamin and Hochberg false discovery rate (FDR) [CITATION_1] and were reported as p c . In addition to the post hoc tests, a total of 26 other statistical tests, which addressed the different metrics and contexts, were included in the FDR corrections. The p-values for the post hoc tests were corrected with the FDR-factor for the Kruskal-Wallis test, and with Bonferroni corrections for the three types of phone tasks.",
